**********************
This is a env_shake prefab
**********************

Q. What is env_shake?
A. env_shake is the thing that shakes the map (or just a bit or it) it is used in alot of ways eg. on a timer or on a trigger.

In this prefab it is on a timer!

It has 3 prefabs in this 

1. shakes all the map.
2. shakes a part of the map.
3. shakes all the map but only shakes physic things and ropes.

So that is this prefab!
hope you like it :D

Thanks.
